他们似乎完全是随机的
They seem completely random.

36
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:47,800
一般来说 当机器给我们 发来像这样的集群时
Usually, when the machine sends us number clusters like this,

37
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:50,800
是有一定联系的
there is some connection.

38
