Would have fixed everything.

544
00:31:51,600 --> 00:31:52,600
那是不对的
It was wrong.

545
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:55,100
我们知道这么做不对
We knew it was wrong.

546
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:59,300
